      "content": "It's definitely a coincidence that the headache came on while you were in a library, considering the intense mental focus you must have been under. Drinking too much coffee and not enough water can indeed cause headaches, but the sudden and intense nature of yours suggests there might be something else at play. I'd recommend taking it easy for the rest of the day, getting plenty of water, and maybe doing some gentle relaxation techniques to help clear your head. If the headache persists or worsens, you can always consult a medical professional for further evaluation.",
