      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. yeah i'll try to drink more water. it was just really scary for a sec because it was so fast. i'm feeling a bit dizzy now too, and my neck feels kinda stiff. u think that's just from the caffeine/dehydration too? it's probably fine right, just stress?",
